snippet.title: Enemy (Female Ver.) || Arcane Cover by Reinaeiry
snippet.description:
"Jinx! All your fault! All your fault!"

Ouch. Also, if a series has sapphic characters (even just a tiny smidgen), I WILL get my grubby little hands on it and I WILL do a song about it. There was a thunderstorm while I recorded this but not even god or nature can stop me from being gay. You're hot, cupcake.
────────────
